defaultia and have widespread industry and public support.  
defaultWe would encourage Government to continue to encourage and support these, and other, solutions.  
defaultHowever, as is clear from our evidence, there are some obvious areas where 
defaultmore robust 
defaultGovernment interven
defaulttion 
defaultis required to ensure proper protection of children online
default, for example online pornography, where currently lack of industry self-regulation is leading to children being able to access inappropriate and potentially harmful content.  
defaultEqually, industry 
defaultcould do more, for example through effective moderation, to ensure that their service is safe for children and the vulnerable online.  
